OL,3,CMan convicted over #1.38m watch
OL,4,Crobbery that 'led manager to kill
OL,5,Chimself'
OL,7,FA man has been been found guilty of
OL,8,Fconspiring to commit a #1.38 million
OL,9,Fwatch robbery at a jewellery store in
OL,10,Fsouth-west London which, a court
OL,11,Fheard, led its manager to take his own
OL,12,Flife.
OL,14,FMannix Pedro, 37, was "closely
OL,15,Finvolved in the planning and
OL,16,Fexecution" of the raid of the 247
OL,17,FKettles shop in Richmond on May 25
OL,18,Flast year, Woolwich Crown Court heard.
