OL,4,Crobbery that 'led manager to kill
OL,5,Chimself'
OL,7,FThe store manager Oliver White, 27,
OL,8,Ftook his own life the next day "as a
OL,9,Fdirect result" of the robbery, in
OL,10,Fwhich more than 70 "high-value"
OL,11,Fwatches were taken, prosecutors said.
OL,13,FNone of the watches stolen in the
OL,14,Frobbery have been recovered, and none
OL,15,Fwere insured, despite the business
OL,16,Fbeing a victim of theft three years
OL,17,Fearlier, jurors were told.
