OL,5,Chimself'
OL,7,FMr White was said to have felt
OL,8,F"extremely upset" about the incident,
OL,9,Fduring which he was tied up and put in
OL,10,Fa headlock.
OL,12,FA jury found Pedro, of Woking, Surrey,
OL,13,Fguilty of the offence on Wednesday by
OL,14,Fa majority verdict of 10 to one, after
OL,15,Fmore than 23 hours of deliberation.
OL,17,FProsecutors said the defendant did not
OL,18,Fgo into the shop during the robbery,
OL,19,Fbut instead organised the use of a
OL,20,Fstolen Audi as one of two getaway cars.
